In [806]:
h = 200
w = 324
v_dis = ['#482575', '#414487', '#35608d', '#2a788e', '#21918d', '#22a884', '#43bf71', '#7ad151', '#bcdf27']

t = alt.Chart(count_url).mark_line(point=True).encode(
    x='Year:O',
    y=alt.Y('Total:Q', scale = alt.Scale(domain = (3500000, 12000000))),
    tooltip = ['Year:O', alt.Tooltip('Total:Q', title = 'Total Records', format = ',.0f')],
    color = alt.value(v_dis[0])
).properties(
    width=w,
    height=h,
    title='Total Number of Records'
)

tp = alt.Chart(count_url).mark_line(point=True).encode(
    x=alt.X('Year:O'),
    y=alt.Y('Total_Paid:Q', title = 'USD', scale = alt.Scale(domain = (500000000, 4000000000)), axis=alt.Axis(format='$,f')),
    tooltip = ['Year:O', alt.Tooltip('Total_Paid:Q', title = 'Amount Paid', format = '$,.2f')],
    color = alt.value(v_dis[4])
).properties(
    width=w,
    height=h,
    title = 'Total Amount Paid'
)

doc = alt.Chart(count_url).mark_line(point=True).encode(
    x='Year:O',
    y=alt.Y('Doctors:Q', scale = alt.Scale(domain = (400000, 700000))),
    tooltip = ['Year:O', alt.Tooltip('Doctors:Q', title = 'Number of Doctors', format = ',.0f')],
    color = alt.value(v_dis[2])

).properties(
    width=w,
    height=h,
    title = 'Number of Doctors Paid'
)

cc = alt.Chart(count_url).mark_line(point=True).encode(
    x='Year:O',
    y=alt.Y('Company_Count:Q', title = 'Number of Companies', scale = alt.Scale(domain = (1300, 1700))),
    tooltip = ['Year:O', alt.Tooltip('Company_Count:Q', title = 'Number of Companies', format = ',.0f')],
    color = alt.value(v_dis[6])
).properties(
    width=w,
    height=h,
    title = 'Companies that Made Payments to Doctors'
)

col1 = alt.vconcat(t, tp)
col2 = alt.vconcat(doc, cc)
all_c = alt.hconcat(col1, col2).configure_point(size=80)
all_c

In [865]:
highlight = alt.selection(type='single', on='mouseover',
                          fields=['Year'], nearest=True)

base = alt.Chart(month_url).mark_line(point = True).encode(
    x=alt.X('Month_w:O',  axis=alt.Axis(title='USD'), sort = ['Jan.', 'Feb.', 'Mar.', 'Apr.', 'May', 'Jun.', 'Jul.', 'Aug.', 'Sep.', 'Oct.', 'Nov.']),
    y=alt.Y('Payment_Sum:Q', axis=alt.Axis(title='Month')),
    color=alt.Color('Year:O', scale=alt.Scale(scheme='viridis')),
    tooltip = ['Year:O', 'Payment_Sum:Q'],
).properties(
    height = 400,
    width = 700,
    title = 'Total Payment Amounts'
)

points = base.mark_circle().encode(
    opacity=alt.value(0.5)
).add_selection(
    highlight
)

lines = base.mark_line().encode(
    size=alt.condition(~highlight, alt.value(1), alt.value(5)),
    opacity=alt.condition(~highlight, alt.value(0.6), alt.value(1))
)

Nature and Form Heatmap¶

In [146]:
w = 100
h = 400
years = ['2014', '2015', '2016', '2017', '2018', '2019']
charts = [None] * (len(years) + 1)
charts[0] = alt.Chart(heat_url, title = '2013').mark_rect().encode(
    x=alt.X('Form:O', axis = alt.Axis(title = ' ')),
    y=alt.Y('Nature:O', axis = alt.Axis(title = ' ')),
    color = alt.Color('Count:Q',scale=alt.Scale(type='log',scheme='viridis')),
    tooltip = ['Form:O', 'Nature:O', alt.Tooltip('Count:Q', title = 'Count', format = ',')],
).properties(
    width = w,
    height = h
).transform_filter(
    datum['Year'] == '2013'
)
for i, year in enumerate(years):
    if(year in ['2014', '2015']):
        w = 100
        h = 400
    else:
        w = 150
        h = 400
    charts[i+1] = alt.Chart(heat_url, title = year).mark_rect().encode(
        x=alt.X('Form:O', axis = alt.Axis(title = ' ')),
        y=alt.Y('Nature:O', axis = alt.Axis(labels = False, title = ' ')),
        color = alt.Color('Count:Q',scale=alt.Scale(type='log',scheme='viridis')),
        tooltip = ['Form:O', 'Nature:O', alt.Tooltip('Count:Q', title = 'Count', format = ',')],
    ).properties(
        width = w,
        height = h
    ).transform_filter(
        datum['Year'] == year
    )
heat_map_chart = alt.hconcat(charts[0], charts[1], charts[2], charts[3], charts[4], charts[5], charts[6]).configure_axis(labelLimit = 0, labelFontSize = 11)
heat_map_chart

    datum['Form'] != 'NA'
).encode(
    x=alt.X('Year:O'),
    y=alt.Y('sum(Payment_Sum):Q', axis = alt.Axis(title = 'Payment Amount', format = '$,.0f')),

    datum['Form'] != 'NA'
).encode(

    selection
).add_selection(
    selection
).properties(

years = ['2014', '2015', '2016', '2017', '2018', '2019']
ds = [state_2014, state_2015, state_2016, state_2017, state_2018, state_2019]
charts = [None] * len(years)
states = alt.topo_feature(data.us_10m.url, 'states')
h = 220
w = 300


def chloro_pc(vari, vari_no_type, dataset, title, wi, he):
    chart = alt.Chart(states).mark_geoshape().encode(
        color=alt.Color(vari, scale=alt.Scale(scheme='viridis')),
        tooltip = [alt.Tooltip(vari, title = 'Count Per 10,000 Residents', format = ',.2f'), 'Name:O']
    ).transform_lookup(
        lookup='id',
        from_=alt.LookupData(dataset, 'id', [vari_no_type, 'Name'])
    ).project(
        type='albersUsa'
    ).properties(
        width=wi,
        height=he,
        title = title
    )
    return chart

for i, year in enumerate(years):
    charts[i] = chloro_pc('Count_per_10000:Q', 'Count_per_10000', ds[i], year, w, h)
    
row1 = alt.hconcat(charts[0], charts[1], charts[2])
row2 = alt.hconcat(charts[3], charts[4], charts[5])
col = alt.vconcat(row1, row2, title = 'Counts of Payments to Doctors per 10,000 Residents').configure_title(align = 'center', anchor = 'middle', fontSize = 18)
map_count = col

years = ['2014', '2015', '2016', '2017', '2018', '2019']
ds = [state_2014, state_2015, state_2016, state_2017, state_2018, state_2019]
charts = [None] * len(years)
states = alt.topo_feature(data.us_10m.url, 'states')
h = 200
w = 300


def chloro_pc(vari, vari_no_type, dataset, title, wi, he):
    chart = alt.Chart(states).mark_geoshape().encode(
        color=alt.Color(vari, scale=alt.Scale(scheme='viridis', domain = (9000, 250000))),
        tooltip = [vari, 'Name:O']
    ).transform_lookup(
        lookup='id',
        from_=alt.LookupData(dataset, 'id', [vari_no_type, 'Name'])
    ).project(
        type='albersUsa'
    ).properties(
        width=wi,
        height=he,
        title = title
    )
    return chart

for i, year in enumerate(years):
    charts[i] = chloro_pc('Sum_per_10000:Q', 'Sum_per_10000', ds[i], year, w, h)
    
row1 = alt.hconcat(charts[0], charts[1], charts[2])
row2 = alt.hconcat(charts[3], charts[4], charts[5])
col = alt.vconcat(row1, row2, title = 'Amount of Payments to Doctors per 10,000 Residents').configure_title(align = 'center', anchor = 'middle', fontSize = 18)
map_amt = col
